    "This path represents the most rudimentary solution, drawing upon a substantial volume of data and imbuing the model with time-series-related knowledge through pre-training.",
    "The second strategy involves fine-tuning based on the LLM framework, wherein corresponding mechanisms are devised to adapt the time series, enabling application to existing language models.",
